data.description: Newly renovated and energy efficient block home marries old Florida charm with modern needs. This adorable, one story block home has had a top to bottom renovation, with a new ROOF, new walls, floors, impact windows, and more.Multiple entrance and exits to the property allows for more flexibilty, with a door off the living area onto the carport, front door and off the main primary bedroom suite.Spacious Lot on almost quarter acre with plenty of room in your own detached storage building for your beach toys! NO HOA community with convenient access to Panama City Downtown, St. Andrews Marina or just a few miles to Panama City Beaches.Please note this home is currently for sale or rent.Measurements approximate, please verify.
